{
  "_comment": [
    "This is an EXAMPLE — copy to .mcp.json (project-level) or merge the",
    "'beams' entry into ~/.claude.json (user-level).  Register it USER-LEVEL",
    "with an ABSOLUTE path if you want the doorbell from any working directory",
    "(e.g. several projects' sessions), replacing './channel/beams-channel.mjs'",
    "with e.g. '/home/you/projects/beams/channel/beams-channel.mjs'.",
    "",
    "After registering, launch with the development flag (required for any",
    "community plugin not yet on Anthropic's channel allowlist):",
    "  claude --dangerously-load-development-channels server:beams",
    "",
    "No port to configure: each session's server takes its own OS-assigned",
    "port automatically, and the watcher is auto-armed to find it (set a channel",
    "token first — see channel/README.md step 2).  Set BEAMS_CHANNEL_PORT only",
    "to pin a fixed port.  See channel/README.md for the full setup."
  ],
  "mcpServers": {
    "beams": {
      "command": "node",
      "args": ["./channel/beams-channel.mjs"]
    }
  }
}
